query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathematica')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('dynamic',
'evaluation',
'export',
'fitting',
'front-end',
'graphics3d',
'image-processing',
'import',
'linear-algebra',
'manipulate',
'probability-or-statistics',
'programming',
'special-functions',
'symbolic');
